  "severity": "Important",
  "description": "FRRouting is free software that manages TCP/IP based routing protocols. It supports BGP4, OSPFv2, OSPFv3, ISIS, RIP, RIPng, PIM, NHRP, PBR, EIGRP and BFD. \n\nSecurity Fix(es):\n\n* frr: denial of service via crafted FlowSpec component (CVE-2026-37457)\n\n* frr: denial of service via crafted BGP UPDATE message (CVE-2026-37459)\n\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS score, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer to the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.",
